  "title": "Accounts assistant",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Responsibilities:</u><br /></p><p><p>Assist in daily accounting operations, including data entry and bookkeeping.</p></p><p><p>Prepare invoices, payment vouchers, and follow up on receivables and payables.</p></p><p><p>Maintain accurate financial records and filing of accounting documents.</p></p><p><p>Support month-end closing and basic financial reporting.</p></p><p><p>Coordinate with vendors, customers, and internal departments on accounts matters.<br /></p><p><u>Requirements:</u><br />Diploma or Degree in Accounting, Finance, or a related field.</p><p><p>Basic knowledge of accounting principles and financial processes.</p></p><p><p>Proficient in MS Excel </p></p><p><p>Good attention to detail and organizational skills.</p></p><p><p>Able to work independently and meet deadlines.</p></p></p>",
